data.description: This one has room for everyone!  This four bedroom home features two full baths upstairs and a half bath downstairs, two separate living rooms, an eat-in kitchen as well as a formal dining room, and a unique 3 car attached garage!  In the kitchen you'll find granite counter tops, a brand new fridge, and two separate pantries!  Don't forget to check out the back yard which is great for get togethers with it's water fountain pond view from the fully fenced rear yard!
